agent-driver - Agent Task Driver

USAGE:
    agent-driver [job1] [job2] ...

DESCRIPTION:
    Drive execution of agent tasks. Runs all available jobs or
    specified jobs. Can run locally or remotely.

ARGUMENTS:
    job1, job2, ...
        Specific jobs to run (optional, defaults to all jobs)

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-agent-remote-host HOST
        Remote host for execution

    -conf-agent-remote-user USER
        Remote user for execution

EXAMPLES:
    agent-driver
    agent-driver job1 job2
    agent-driver --option=value
